My recommendation: Stay close to your gate because their loudspeakers aren't very...loud  They have Free WiFi!  I've been to a lot of airports and PHX is definitely not one of my favorite.  Food, drink, and amenities at this airport are seriously lacking.  These are all important factors to consider when you have a delay or layover and want something decent to eat.  Stay away from eating in the sports bars in this airport.  But all of what I'm saying really probably doesn't really matter since who really has any choice in airport these days anyways!

