My recommendation: rack of lamb!  When a good french restaurant does rack of lamb...YUM, don't miss it!  I ate here while on business in Scottsdale and had a very enjoyable time.  Service was a bit slower than I would have liked, but it may have been because I did not decide to have a glass of wine with my meal.  Excellent bread and spread though!  Petite Maison is tucked away on a side street and can be a little bit hard to find (hole in a wall).  Atmosphere was very accommodating though and both their indoor and outdoor seating are super comfortable.

